      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOONLIGHT ZIPPER (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind What's The Story (22.91) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature in the finish again. ROAD TO JERRY'S (8) had been in great form, scoring back to wins before copping a check last time and finishing fourth (23.97), beaten 9 lengths in a Grade 5 at this track. Expected to feature on best form. TRAIN OF THOUGHT (2) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (23.07) at this track over 400m. Drawn well off an inside draw. Rates a leading chance again. KISS AND RUN (6) can run a bold race on best form.",
